ofile_images/1321124227215491072/pIC0lG5M_normal.jpg", "displayName": "ThePersistence", "username": "ScottPresler"}, "content": "If anyone has connections with St. Lawrence Island in Alaska, please message me. \n\nI may have to visit.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 2768}, "likes": 9}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBvN1xa6", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 26, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8736642, "raw_content": "> Representatives shall be apportioned among the several States according to their respective numbers, counting the whole number of persons in each State, excluding Indians not taxed. But when the right to vote at any election for the choice of electors for President and Vice-President of the United States, Representatives in Congress, the Executive and Judicial officers of a State, or the members of the Legislature thereof, is denied to any of the male inhabitants of such State, being twenty-one years of age, and citizens of the United States, or in any way abridged, except for participation in rebellion, or other crime, the basis of representation therein shall be reduced in the proportion which the number of such male citizens shall bear to the whole number of male citizens twenty-one years of age in such State\r\n\r\n\r\nNow, read that back. If any male over the age of 21 is denied the right to vote or has that right abridged somehow, the representation is reduced for the whole state. Hmmm\u2026. Allowing illegal aliens to vote in elections is denying citizens the right to vote. You are denying them their right to vote by canceling it out. Therefore, any blue state that allows illegals to vote, read the amendment, even at the state level, should have their representation reduced to solely the men over the age of 21 in that state. We should be using this against any state that allows illegals to vote in local elections.", "author": "lefty295", "created": 1784467618498, "profile_picture": "NWbNd6AomP4v", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "tomthung", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "14th amendment, section 2. Why aren\u2019t we using this against blue states?", "last_comment_created": 1784475505640, "content": "<blockquote>\n<p>Representatives shall be apportioned among the several States according to their respective numbers, counting the whole number of persons in each State, excluding Indians not taxed. But when the right to vote at any election for the choice of electors for President and Vice-President of the United States, Representatives in Congress, the Executive and Judicial officers of a State, or the members of the Legislature thereof, is denied to any of the male inhabitants of such State, being twenty-one years of age, and citizens of the United States, or in any way abridged, except for participation in rebellion, or other crime, the basis of representation therein shall be reduced in the proportion which the number of such male citizens shall bear to the whole number of male citizens twenty-one years of age in such State</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Now, read that back. If any male over the age of 21 is denied the right to vote or has that right abridged somehow, the representation is reduced for the whole state. Hmmm\u2026. Allowing illegal aliens to vote in elections is denying citizens the right to vote. You are denying them their right to vote by canceling it out. Therefore, any blue state that allows illegals to vote, read the amendment, even at the state level, should have their representation reduced to solely the men over the age of 21 in that state. We should be using this against any state that allows illegals to vote in local elections.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 26, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBvN1xNo", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 27, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8736618, "raw_content": "", "author": "kek_saved_the_world", "created": 1784466839121, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Brownwaterboys", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBvN1xNo.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/HLupy89SDKOA.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/hz5aCjz9CWplKsHQ.png", "width": 768, "content-type": "png", "height": 652}], "blurhash": "U6D9#L~D00Xn8_adf+bb00Xm~qrqo~S5-pxZ", "full_resolution": [956, 1126]}, "title": "There is a reason why you NEVER see its face.", "last_comment_created": 1784475736008, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 6, "score_up": 27, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBvN1xW3", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 26, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8736637, "raw_content":